body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, my name is Timothy Wilson and I am a Customer Service Representative at XYZ Car Dealership. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello Timothy, my name is Dorothy Flores.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Dorothy. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling nervous about the car purchase process.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your concerns. Can you please provide me with the last four digits of your phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's seven eight two zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. To better assist you, could you also share the model of the car you are interested in purchasing?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm looking to buy the Blue Sedan 2021.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great choice! Thank you for sharing that information, Dorothy. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, thank you. That's all for now.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for reaching out, Dorothy. If you have any further questions, feel free to contact me. Have a wonderful day!
